{'message': "Thank you for your feedback, Bart. As we explained in our previous communications, cookies are intended to personalize your online experience and add to your convenience when using our website. We have a strict privacy policy that includes our promise never to sell, trade, or export our customers' information to any party beyond our organization. You can view our privacy policy in full here: https://mountainroseherbs.com/policies/privacy-policy/

