{'message': 'Thank you for your feedback. We are sorry to hear that the peppermint essential oil you ordered did not meet your expectations. Mountain Rose Herbs’ organic peppermint essential oil is a 100% steam distillation of the Peppermint plant, Mentha piperita. Due to natural variation, botanicals of the same genus and species can differ in the concentration of their constituents, which can cause the same plant to have different aromatic properties. As our Claims & Returns Team explained, the lot you received is sourced from the United States and has a greener and grassier profile than previous lots we have offered from India or Hungary.

We want to reassure you that this product has been thoroughly inspected by our Quality Control Team and was indeed found to meet all of our specifications as well as pass identity testing. As one of the first herbal products companies to establish and run a full microbial and analytical lab onsite, we have always been committed to providing high quality botanical products to our customers from a source they can trust.

Our Claims & Returns Team was happy to offer multiple options for resolution. We are sorry if this was not satisfactory. Please let us know if you have any additional questions that we may be able to help with or if we can assist you with anything else. Wishing you all the best! ~ Erin', 'publishedDate': '2024-06-05T16:20:49.000Z', 'updatedDate': None}

