Should you wish to return the Red Clover Herb you ordered, you are welcome to do so within 30 days of the date your package was delivered. You can find our full return instructions here: https://mountainroseherbs.com/return-policy/ 

We hope this provides some clarification regarding the order you received! Warmly ~ Erin ', 'publishedDate': '2024-06-13T22:05:03.000Z', 'updatedDate': None}

