{'message': "Proposition 65 is a unique California law requiring businesses to include a warning on any products that contain quantifiable amounts of over nine hundred possible chemicals. Due to the unique nature of this state-specific law, which only applies to California, we are obligated to place a Prop 65 warning sticker on all products being shipped to that state. In addition to this, we do share information about this warning in an information box that requires customers to accept before proceeding to check out. We are truly sorry if this information was missed when placing your order. 

We assure you that our products are safe, and we thoroughly test all of them to comply with federal and industry standards for safety. You can find more information about this law on the American Herbal Product's Association website found here: https://www.ahpa.org/content.asp?contentid=165

Unfortunately, the most recent emails or chats we could find using the email address associated with your order were from 2022. You can always feel free to contact our Customer Service team via email at support@mountainroseherbs.com or by phone at 1-800-879-3337, Monday -Friday, between the hours of 8 am-4 pm, Pacific Time. We are happy to provide more information about Proposition 65, as well as our testing and Quality Control practices. ~Juniper", 'publishedDate': '2024-08-08T21:03:32.000Z', 'updatedDate': None}

